{"tid":30957,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「葉劉概念股」飛升 浩德控股尾市漲近一成","createTime":"2016-12-09T11:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T16:20:57.000Z","uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b92adf5c72e9134bbd2f2dbefa7dc0f66902b0a","tid":30957,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:38:29.000Z","msg":"行政長官梁振英宣布不競逐連任，「葉劉概念股」隨即飛升，有意參選下屆特首選舉的葉劉淑儀，其姪兒旗下的浩德控股（8149），尾市急升近一成。<br />\n<br />\n浩德控股在10月底配售上市，大股東葉天賜，為葉劉淑儀的姪兒。該股昨日在3點半後，即梁振英宣布不連任後，一度急升14％，收市報0.42元， 升9.09%。<br />\n<br />\n不過，該股在今年10月配售上市時，以每股0.425元配售上市，雖然上市後曾急升至逾8元，但其後大幅插水，今日雖急升近一成，收市價仍未返回上市時的定價。<br />\n<br />\n浩德控股主要經營企業融資及物業投資業務，向客戶提供保薦、財務顧問及合規顧問服務，同時在日本及香港投資房地產。<br />\n<br />\n記者：廖毅然<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1481271302211&amp;issue=20161209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1481271302211%26issue%3D20161209&d=ZETiPhJ0t%2B%2BGroWVQ6EUKaEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=93527df5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1481271302211&amp;issue=20161209</a>"},{"pid":"01140f95a1d3a07fd8d578da40e16a036bb76cda","tid":30957,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:49:14.000Z","msg":"d 炒家真係好勁 ... 點解可以記得哂 D 人物關係 ... 即市就可以炒起  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9906e6a065fc92c0ac5bba28d800a8e0010b10c0","tid":30957,"uid":88,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d 炒家真係好勁 ... 點解可以記得哂 D 人物關係 ... 即市就可以炒起  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有人放料囉即係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847a5567d4846b4083407d46a9b4c9a3b0800d28","tid":30957,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:54:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>d 炒家真係好勁 ... 點解可以記得哂 D 人物關係 ...